nish; also to rehearse","kjv_def":"make mention; be mindful, remember","pos":"verb","usage":"remember(19x)"},"G3403":{"id":"G3403","lemma":"μιμνήσκω","translit":"mimnḗskō","derivation":"a prolonged form of G3415 (μνάομαι) (from which some of the tenses are borrowed);","strongs_def":"to remind, i.e. (middle voice) to recall to mind","kjv_def":"be mindful, remember","pos":"verb","usage":"remember(1x)"},"G3442":{"id":"G3442","lemma":"μονόφθαλμος","translit":"monóphthalmos","derivation":"from G3441 (μόνος) and G3788 (ὀφθαλμός);","strongs_def":"one-eyed","kjv_def":"with one eye","pos":"adjective"},"G3436":{"id":"G3436","lemma":"μολυσμός","translit":"molysmós","derivation":"from G3435 (μολύνω);","strongs_def":"a stain; i.e. (figuratively) immorality","kjv_def":"filthiness"},"G3433":{"id":"G3433","lemma":"μόλις","translit":"mólis","derivation":"probably by variation for G3425 (μόγις);","strongs_def":"with difficulty","kjv_def":"hardly, scarce(-ly), + with much work","pos":"adverb","usage":"scarce(2x), scarcely(2x), hardly(1x)"},"G3425":{"id":"G3425","lemma":"μόγις","translit":"mógis","derivation":"adverb from a primary (toil);","strongs_def":"with difficulty","kjv_def":"hardly","pos":"adverb","usage":"hardly(1x)"},"G3447":{"id":"G3447","lemma":"μοσχοποιέω","translit":"moschopoiéō","derivation":"from G3448 (μόσχος) and G4160 (ποιέω);","strongs_def":"to fabricate the image of a bullock","kjv_def":"make a calf","pos":"verb"},"G3439":{"id":"G3439","lemma":"μονογενής","translit":"monogenḗs","derivation":"from G3441 (μόνος) and G1096 (γίνομαι);","strongs_def":"only-born, i.e. sole","kjv_def":"only (begotten, child)","pos":"adjective","usage":"only(2x)"},"G3474":{"id":"G3474","lemma":"μωρός","translit":"mōrós","derivation":"probably from the base of G3466 (μυστήριον);","strongs_def":"dull or stupid (as if shut up), i.e. heedless, (morally) blockhead, (apparently) absurd","kjv_def":"fool(-ish, X -ishness)","pos":"adjective","usage":"foolish(7x), fool(5x), foolishness(1x)"},"G3412"